short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Innovator browser extension which improving work with Start Item functionality

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Support “Start Item” functionality when you try to open new window with Item link and then you should close opened window and go to the main Innovator page. Extension will find main Innovator window and switch focus on opened Item (and close previous window which you try to open). For use with the Innovator Browser.
